estimates store f2
ivregress 2sls hoursfem  agefirstborn   femhead_hh substrat (size = secondoldestgirl ) if size>1, robust
estimates store f3

ivregress 2sls hoursfem  agefirstborn   femhead_hh substrat (size = percentfmales ), robust
estimates store f4

ivreg2 hoursfem  agefirstborn   femhead_hh substrat (size = oldestgirl secondoldestgirl percentfmales ) if size>1, robust liml
ivreg2 hoursmale  agefirstborn   femhead_hh substrat (size = oldestgirl secondoldestgirl percentfmales ) if size>1, robust liml

ivreg2 hourschld  agefirstborn   femhead_hh substrat (size = oldestgirl secondoldestgirl percentfmales ) if size>1, robust liml

 regress hoursmale size agefirstborn femhead_hh substrat, robust
 estimates store m1
